Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.73,0:00:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了要拯救世界的所有一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.47,0:00:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脱离走向毁灭的大崩落危机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.77,0:00:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不断旅行的里德，法拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.01,0:00:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔  梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.21,0:00:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在旅途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.64,0:00:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停留的海上都市·贝鲁卡纽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.98,0:00:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充满了许多的迷团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.55,0:00:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲在地下的“奈雷特福音”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.78,0:00:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的目的到底是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.88,0:00:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有等待里德他们的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.25,0:00:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又将会如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.76,0:00:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样…故事已渐入佳境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.23,0:00:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第12话  制裁之楔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.18,0:00:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？  你在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.98,0:00:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么哭得那么伤心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.75,0:00:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.66,0:01:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你终于醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.64,0:01:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得你是那天在酒店里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.91,0:01:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说话的那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.81,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴你还记得我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.87,0:01:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是反艾克丝西亚同盟的医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.54,0:01:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反艾克丝西亚同盟？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.72,0:01:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我们同盟的基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.72,0:01:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你爸爸…塔斯帖克·布鲁卡诺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.39,0:01:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留给我们的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.53,0:01:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.59,0:01:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.69,0:01:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隐瞒是赛雷斯提亚人后裔这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.30,0:01:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直生活到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.27,0:01:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…家族里有茵费利亚人的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.80,0:01:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今也有不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.44,0:01:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去在这个镇的后面不远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.21,0:01:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾经有个小村庄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.94,0:01:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里是供那些人居住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.25,0:01:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久在茵费利亚这块大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.88,0:02:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛雷斯提亚人便被遗忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.92,0:02:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我们就当作奇怪的茵费利亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.65,0:02:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐被这里的人民所接纳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.06,0:02:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是塔斯帖克总是这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.13,0:02:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以这样继续下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.06,0:02:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要让我们能够公开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.43,0:02:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在茵费利亚生活才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此这时候也只有打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.80,0:02:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被复仇心迷住的艾克丝西亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.41,0:02:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯帖克在被赶出这座岛之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.75,0:02:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还把拥有茵费利亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且托付给我们一样东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.52,0:02:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一样东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.09,0:02:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拿来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.65,0:02:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.99,0:02:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.76,0:02:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.80,0:02:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在哭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.91,0:03:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在做梦吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.55,0:03:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制裁之楔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个是奈雷特福音的最后王牌吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.88,0:03:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.82,0:03:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之所以要抢夺大晶灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.55,0:03:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也都是为了要重建制裁之楔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.96,0:03:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大战时期…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.06,0:03:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为晶灵仪表毁损
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.43,0:03:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像就一直无法使用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.76,0:03:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才想利用大晶灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.10,0:03:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来补其不足啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.87,0:03:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那股力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.24,0:03:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说足以摧毁一座山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.34,0:03:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结合三大晶灵的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再藉由机器增幅的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确是有那种可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.58,0:03:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茵费利亚城要是被那种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.25,0:03:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻击到的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.48,0:03:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错  根本就不是对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.82,0:03:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.25,0:03:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有看到巴鲁沙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.89,0:03:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦，我说法拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.39,0:03:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是管它的时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.20,0:03:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.97,0:04:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.21,0:04:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着  你还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…别这样好了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  玛萝妮的脸好红哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.25,0:04:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是所谓的禁忌之爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.02,0:04:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.02,0:04:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.36,0:04:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  差不多该放开我了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不~要~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动力炉达到临界点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.52,0:04:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启动作业继续进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.22,0:04:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是反艾克丝西亚同盟托给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.99,0:04:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.26,0:04:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是古文书的抄本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.59,0:05:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我爸爸在脱离奈雷特福音前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.96,0:05:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把艾克丝西亚珍藏的古文书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.67,0:05:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷地抄写下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.90,0:05:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸认为对艾克丝西亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起义的行动早晚都会来到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.27,0:05:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想说这应该会派得上用场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.31,0:05:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们和同盟的人也都看过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.48,0:05:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面虽然写的是晶灵语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不晓得怎么搞的就是看不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.15,0:05:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同盟的人们认为那篇文章里面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.19,0:05:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该隐藏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.36,0:05:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与奈雷特福音有关的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.56,0:05:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看…看得懂吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全看不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.47,0:05:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也完全看不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.54,0:05:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看得懂吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要马上解读出来是不可能的事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过所有的暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.51,0:05:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都一定有它的基础性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.68,0:05:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要花点时间的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.22,0:05:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是解读的出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.89,0:06:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是能解读那篇文章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.72,0:06:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并得到线索的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.16,0:06:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许就可以从艾克丝西亚手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.22,0:06:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夺回大晶灵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.33,0:06:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！这个方法…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行得通  行得通对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.13,0:06:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你别抢我的话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.13,0:06:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然  同盟也会协助里德你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.11,0:06:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？  是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.38,0:06:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启动制裁之楔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.44,0:06:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在启动还太勉强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.28,0:06:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类的力量还真是没用呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.42,0:06:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祖先的御灵啊  彷徨不已的憎恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在吾力量之笼罩下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.09,0:06:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为吾之眷属吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.77,0:06:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在艾克丝西亚的祈祷下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.87,0:06:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而实体化的这些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.97,0:06:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是过去命丧于这片土地上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.14,0:06:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛雷斯提亚人的怨灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.61,0:06:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死后也不忘怨恨茵费利亚的他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经毫无一丝的人性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可说是只有憎恨而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.05,0:07:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.59,0:07:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让制裁之楔复活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.06,0:07:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制裁之楔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.15,0:07:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在正式复活的时刻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.82,0:07:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.60,0:07:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.57,0:07:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快看那个！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.01,0:08:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海…海啸要过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.98,0:08:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家快往高处逃啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.42,0:08:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也快去避难吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家动作快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.46,0:08:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们谁来搞定这家伙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.53,0:08:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂是看破了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.52,0:08:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快看那个！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.77,0:09:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,污蔑我们的神明为邪神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并建立虚伪历史的茵费利亚人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是你们赎罪的时刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.98,0:09:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祖先们所遗留下来的这制裁之楔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.88,0:09:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将会替我们毁灭茵费利亚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.85,0:09:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.75,0:09:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制裁之楔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.92,0:09:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的城镇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.93,0:09:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.25,0:09:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚大人她已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.89,0:09:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.16,0:09:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这样对我们？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.13,0:10:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经被复仇所蒙盖住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.60,0:10:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝鲁卡纽会变成什么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.90,0:10:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会变成什么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.74,0:10:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她都已经不管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里德他们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.94,0:10:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前往反艾克丝西亚同盟的基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.11,0:10:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决定去投靠他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.32,0:10:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太惨了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.14,0:10:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们都平安无事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.27,0:10:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.67,0:10:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你们帮了我不少忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.91,0:10:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过…能动的只有我这个老头子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.08,0:10:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又失去了一道希望之光啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.42,0:11:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样…就只剩下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.96,0:11:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经解读完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.13,0:11:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.57,0:11:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有关一个少女的悲伤故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那名少女在战乱之世结束后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.81,0:11:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是被遗留在异国的人民之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.74,0:11:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回祖国之路被断绝的他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.01,0:11:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在战乱结束之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.92,0:11:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更是希望敌国能灭亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.69,0:11:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了把这个愿望传达给后代子孙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们创造出永恒的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.69,0:11:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其身似有似无
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其心似人非人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.83,0:11:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管经过几千年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依旧憎恨所恨之事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.00,0:11:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到宿愿结束为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.64,0:11:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少女自行走出来奉献她的肉体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.38,0:11:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其身仍保有生命的沉入地底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而灵魂则一分为二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.82,0:12:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后…永恒的生命就此诞生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.52,0:12:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个故事是这样解释的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.92,0:12:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在过去的战争时期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.59,0:12:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲藏在这贝鲁卡纽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.89,0:12:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛雷斯提亚士兵们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.83,0:12:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了把对敌国茵费利亚的怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.40,0:12:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传给后世子孙知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.10,0:12:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此便创造出虚假的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.74,0:12:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.67,0:12:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是利用晶灵技术…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.54,0:12:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你解释简单一点好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.58,0:12:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的想法跟她们一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.68,0:12:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  简单来说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.88,0:12:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是从人心抽出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.45,0:12:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对茵费利亚的仇恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.72,0:12:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后再应用晶灵技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.69,0:12:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来诞生出新的生命体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.09,0:12:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果在那个计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.69,0:12:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,选中了一名少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.31,0:13:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据以上情况所提出来的结论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.58,0:13:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩正是艾克丝西亚的本体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.91,0:13:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.85,0:13:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.08,0:13:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得我爷爷的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷他们那一代的领主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.89,0:13:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像也是艾克丝西亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.95,0:13:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是有认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.89,0:13:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是利用什么晶灵技术…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.13,0:13:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说艾克丝西亚不是人类？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.33,0:13:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么那个被埋在地底的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.60,0:13:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果怎样了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕还没有死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.77,0:13:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是艾克丝西亚的本体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然艾克丝西亚有在活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.61,0:13:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就表示那名少女还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.88,0:13:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好那个少女…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.75,0:13:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是出现在梦中的那个女孩吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.52,0:13:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道她？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.15,0:13:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮你也梦到啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.32,0:13:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我们也有梦到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.45,0:13:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们到底在讲什么？  不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.76,0:13:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说只有赛雷斯提亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.63,0:13:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才梦到那女孩子啰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.70,0:14:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.24,0:14:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我觉得她好可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.84,0:14:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一直一直都是自己一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.68,0:14:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实在是太可怜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.34,0:14:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在梦里的确一直哭着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.95,0:14:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩…现在会是在哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，普拉提亚小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.45,0:14:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在制裁之楔的里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有一个只有首领
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能进去的房间吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.66,0:14:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经你这么一提…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.99,0:14:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难不成…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.13,0:14:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,献身给奈雷特神这两千年以来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.50,0:14:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于走到这个阶段了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.47,0:14:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.10,0:14:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都不准任何人接近这女孩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们说什么都要去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.28,0:14:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.15,0:14:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只靠我们这些人闯入制裁之楔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.82,0:14:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确是太鲁莽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.22,0:14:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是也只有现在能这么做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.99,0:15:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们…也希望能和你们一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.80,0:15:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带路这件事…就包在我身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.57,0:15:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也希望帮上什么忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.84,0:15:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过同志们都受了伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.20,0:15:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一派得上用场的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.97,0:15:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又只有我这个老头子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.91,0:15:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.74,0:15:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.94,0:15:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，怎么都没看到里德大人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.51,0:15:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法拉也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.55,0:15:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在人数越多越好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.05,0:15:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起去找他们吧  好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.55,0:15:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必去找他们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.43,0:15:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.80,0:15:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.37,0:15:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，法拉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.97,0:15:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯我只是想起一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.81,0:15:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们刚到贝鲁卡纽的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.71,0:15:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实距离现在也没多久而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.98,0:15:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是总觉得好像是很久以前的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.68,0:15:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过…这一切也快结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.05,0:15:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.25,0:15:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等夺回大晶灵之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.19,0:16:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们将再继续未完的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到法罗斯山去找光之桥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后从那里去赛雷斯提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.93,0:16:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.90,0:16:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了这个  我们得努力才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.07,0:16:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦，葵吉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.94,0:16:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.74,0:16:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.88,0:16:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，你们误会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.45,0:16:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,误会了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经清醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让我们帮忙好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.22,0:16:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.12,0:16:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎里德他们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又得到了新伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.66,0:16:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后…命运的早晨来临了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位  我们走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.01,0:16:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.14,0:16:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你们好运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.88,0:16:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也会加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.18,0:16:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.58,0:17:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.45,0:17:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔，你的晕船毛病没问题吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.98,0:17:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在飞行训练的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.42,0:17:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪的   感觉就没那么不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.26,0:17:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会那样啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是他有心要拼命的关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.59,0:17:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这不符合理论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.43,0:17:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也这么认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你的啰  基尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.00,0:17:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈雷特神…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.24,0:17:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，两国的神明请保佑他们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.71,0:17:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…  怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.25,0:17:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得太安静了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.42,0:17:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得事情有点不对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.02,0:17:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家小心点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.85,0:17:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨的灵魂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.12,0:17:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请与我合而为一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.26,0:17:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化为巨大的力量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.60,0:17:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…！  什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.41,0:17:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是长距离晶灵炮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.11,0:18:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家快逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.15,0:18:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来不及了！  快跳船！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.80,0:18:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…这就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长距离晶灵炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.07,0:18:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威力实在太惊人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.04,0:18:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制裁之楔…终于重建完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.48,0:18:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而它的存在实在是太强大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.15,0:18:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里德他们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.15,0:18:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是否能阻止艾克丝西亚的野心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待…最后精彩好戏
